From 8496f1be111cae9bfc4dabe2aafe4af44e81d807 Mon Sep 17 00:00:00 2001
From: "Ryan X. Charles" <ryan@ryanxcharles.com>
Date: Sat, 30 May 2026 21:48:49 -0500
Subject: [PATCH 71/84] Deny permissions by default

A shell once handed out keys,
To every bright API breeze.
Now TermSurf says "no,"
Unless features can show
A safe path with tests that appease.
